<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <link
            href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
            rel="stylesheet"
            integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        />
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="../favicon/S.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/mypage.css" />
        <title>SoonGV</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-body-tertiary nav-underline">
                <div class="container-fluid">
                    <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"><p id="pppp">SoonGV</p></a>
                    <button
                        class="navbar-toggler"
                        type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                        data-bs-target="#navbarNavDropdown"
                        aria-controls="navbarNavDropdown"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-label="Toggle navigation"
                    >
                        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                    </button>
                    <div
                        class="collapse navbar-collapse"
                        id="navbarNavDropdown"
                    >
                        <ul class="navbar-nav">
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" aria-current="page" href="/"
                                    >영화</a
                                >
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="/reservation">예매</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="#">이벤트</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                                <a
                                    class="nav-link dropdown-toggle"
                                    href="#"
                                    role="button"
                                    data-bs-toggle="dropdown"
                                    aria-expanded="false"
                                >
                                    스토어
                                </a>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                                    <li>
                                        <a class="dropdown-item" href="#"
                                            >팝콘</a
                                        >
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <a class="dropdown-item" href="#"
                                            >콤보</a
                                        >
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <a class="dropdown-item" href="#"
                                            >음료</a
                                        >
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display: flex">
                        <% if(islogged){%>
                        <a
                            href="/mypage"
                            style="cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none"
                            ><p>마이 페이지</p></a
                        >
                        <a
                            href="/logout"
                            style="cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none"
                            ><p>로그아웃</p></a
                        >
                        <%}else{%>
                        <a
                            href="/signup"
                            style="
                                cursor: pointer;
                                text-decoration-line: none;
                                margin-right: 1vw;
                            "
                            ><p>회원가입</p></a
                        >
                        <a
                            href="/login"
                            style="cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none"
                            ><p>로그인</p></a
                        >
                        <%}%>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <div id="contents">
            <div id="list" style="width: 300px">
                <h3>마이페이지</h3>
                <hr />
                <ul id="snb">
                    <a href="#">MY CGV HOME</a
                    ><br />
                    <a href="#">나의 예매내역</a>
                    <li><a>신용카드 영수증 출력</a></li>
                    <a>관람권/할인쿠폰 관리</a>
                    <li id="credit">
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <a> 영화관람권 </a>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <a> 할인쿠폰 </a>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <a> 기프트카드 </a>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <a> 카드사 할인쿠폰 </a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div id="menu"></div>
            </div>
            <div id="listContent" style="width: 500px">
                <table style="border: 1px solid black">
                    <tr style="background-color: #5ab">
                        <td>일시</td>
                        <td>좌석</td>
                    </tr>
                    <%if(data){%> <% data.reverse().forEach(element => {%>
                    <%const reserved_at = element.reservation_at%> <%const
                    reservedDate =
                    `${reserved_at.getFullYear()}-${reserved_at.getMonth()+1}-${reserved_at.getDate()}`;%>
                    <%const reservedTime = `${reserved_at.getHours()}시
                    ${reserved_at.getMinutes()}분
                    ${reserved_at.getSeconds()}초`;%>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <p>
                                DATE : <%= reservedDate%><br />TIME :
                                <%=reservedTime%>
                            </p>
                            <p></p>
                        </td>

                        <td>
                            <p><%=element.reserved_seats%></p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <%})} %>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="footer" style="margin-top: 65vh">
            <p>대표: OOO 사업자등록번호:XXX - XX - XXXXX</p>
            <p>통신판매업신고번호 2024-경기안산-XXXX</p>
            <p>© SOONGV. All Rights Reserved</p>
        </div>
        <script
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        ></script>
        <script>
            const islogged = '<%= islogged%>';
        </script>
        <script type="text/javascript" src="../js/mypage.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>
